<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 13:03:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>合并黑洞和引力波的可视化</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/visualization-of-merging-black-holes-and-gravitational-waves</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 13:03:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/visualization-of-merging-black-holes-and-gravitational-waves</guid></item><item><title>TESS 刚刚以一种新的方式发现了一颗行星——八年的数据中可能隐藏着更多的东西</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/tess-just-found-a-planet-in-a-new-way-and-more-may-be-hiding-in-its-eight-years-of-data</link><description>美国宇航局的 TESS（凌日系外行星勘测卫星）任务首次通过时空扭曲识别出一颗绕遥远恒星运行的行星。与 TESS 定期揭示的环绕恒星的凌日行星不同，新发现的微透镜世界是一颗远离其主恒星运行的超级木星。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/tess-just-found-a-planet-in-a-new-way-and-more-may-be-hiding-in-its-eight-years-of-data.gif" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 12:48:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/tess-just-found-a-planet-in-a-new-way-and-more-may-be-hiding-in-its-eight-years-of-data</guid></item><item><title>人工智能工具改进了对谁将对癌症免疫治疗药物产生反应的预测</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/ai-tool-improves-prediction-of-who-will-respond-to-cancer-immunotherapy-drugs</link><description>被称为免疫检查点抑制剂（ICIs）的癌症免疫治疗药物可以成为癌症患者的神奇药物，可以治愈一些癌症患者，并将另一些患者的致命疾病转变为可控制的慢性病。但这些药物只对一小部分患者有效，而且几乎没有迹象表明其原因——这种知识差距会对患者预后、临床试验招募和可能带来新疗法的研究产生不利影响。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ai-tool-improves-prediction-of-who-will-respond-to-cancer-immunotherapy-drugs2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 12:33:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/ai-tool-improves-prediction-of-who-will-respond-to-cancer-immunotherapy-drugs</guid></item><item><title>这种堆叠式 CFET 架构是终极 CMOS 平台吗？</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/is-this-stacked-cfet-architecture-the-ultimate-cmos-platform</link><description>IBM选择了与英特尔、三星、台积电不同的道路。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/is-this-stacked-cfet-architecture-the-ultimate-cmos-platform2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 12:18:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/is-this-stacked-cfet-architecture-the-ultimate-cmos-platform</guid></item><item><title>科学家发现帕金森病如何在大脑中传播以及减缓它的方法</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-discover-how-parkinsons-may-spread-in-brain-and-way-to-slow-it</link><description>耶鲁大学的一位研究人员告诉《新闻周刊》，一个新确定的帕金森病目标已经在试验中进行测试。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/scientists-discover-how-parkinsons-may-spread-in-brain-and-way-to-slow-it.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 12:03:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/scientists-discover-how-parkinsons-may-spread-in-brain-and-way-to-slow-it</guid></item><item><title>一项有 200 年历史的物理实验可以帮助建造未来的计算机</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/a-200-year-old-physics-experiment-could-help-build-future-computers</link><description>新加坡南洋理工大学 (NTU Singapore) 的科学家们通过复兴 200 多年前的经典光学实验，找到了一种更简单的方法来产生被称为光学斯格明子的不寻常光结构。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-200-year-old-physics-experiment-could-help-build-future-computers.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 11:48:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/a-200-year-old-physics-experiment-could-help-build-future-computers</guid></item><item><title>冰冷的冥王星上发现六处大规模山体滑坡</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/six-massive-landslides-discovered-on-icy-pluto</link><description>科学家首次发现冥王星上发生山体滑坡的证据。一张纸&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/six-massive-landslides-discovered-on-icy-pluto.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 11:33:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/six-massive-landslides-discovered-on-icy-pluto</guid></item><item><title>通过激光焊接固定用于储存化学废物的玻璃容器</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/secure-glass-containers-for-storing-chemical-waste-through-laser-welding</link><description>随着电动汽车的采用不断增长，对电池材料和工业化学废物的安全和永久存储的需求也在不断增长。某些废物流需要在所谓的 IV 类垃圾填埋场进行处置，这对储存容器提出了特别严格的要求。这些必须同时确保环境保护、安全处理和长期结构完整性。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/secure-glass-containers-for-storing-chemical-waste-through-laser-welding.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 11:18:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/secure-glass-containers-for-storing-chemical-waste-through-laser-welding</guid></item><item><title>解决有关神秘超导材料的 30 年来的难题</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/solving-a-30-year-old-puzzle-about-a-mysterious-superconducting-material</link><description>一种由钇、钡和氧化铜制成的材料（更广为人知的名称是 YBCO）自 1987 年被发现以来就引起了科学家们的兴趣，主要是因为它在高于正常温度的情况下仍能保持超导特性。然而，它非常脆，这使得它很难投入实际使用。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/solving-a-30-year-old-puzzle-about-a-mysterious-superconducting-material.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 11:03:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/solving-a-30-year-old-puzzle-about-a-mysterious-superconducting-material</guid></item><item><title>世界上第一个超导量子热机为更大的量子计算机提供了途径</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/worlds-first-superconducting-quantum-heat-engine-offers-path-to-larger-quantum-computers</link><description>最近我们对热力学原理在量子领域如何应用的理解的进步可以促进量子技术的发展，而对量子热力学的更清晰的了解反过来可以增强我们对经典热力学的理解。现在，阿尔托大学的研究人员展示了超导电路内的第一个循环量子热机。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/worlds-first-superconducting-quantum-heat-engine-offers-path-to-larger-quantum-computers2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 10:48:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/worlds-first-superconducting-quantum-heat-engine-offers-path-to-larger-quantum-computers</guid></item></channel></rss>